h1 LocalSense
p Yep.

h2 Overall Progress: #{totals.progress}%
.progress.progress-striped.active
  .bar(style="width: #{totals.progress}%")
div History: #{totals.history}

h2 Wall of Shame
ol
  - each shamedUser in shamedUsers
    li <strong>#{shamedUser.username}</strong> with <strong>#{shamedUser.open_issues}</strong> open issues.

h2 Milestones
ol
  - each milestone in milestones
    li
      strong.pull-right due #{milestone.due_on}
      h3 #{milestone.title}: [#{milestone.open_issues}/#{milestone.closed_issues}] #{milestone.progress}%
      .progress.progress-striped
        .bar(style="width: #{milestone.progress}%")
      div History: #{milestone.history}
